abstract: MEMPHIS, June 4 -- Ben Hogan's game collapsed in the heat today, allowing J.C. Goosie and Bill Collins to take the lead with three-round totals of 203's in the $30,000 Memphis open golf tournament.

abstract: FORT WORTH, May 15 (AP) -- Julius Boros sank a 20-foot birdie putt on the seventeenth hole today for a one-stroke victory in the $30,000 Colonial National invitation golf tournament. He had 280 for seventy-two holes.
